Package: waddR
Type: Package
Title: Statistical Test for One-Dimensional Distributions Based on the Wasserstein Metric
Version: 0.1
Date: 2019-06-17
Author: Roman Schefzik <r.schefzik@dkfz-heidelberg.de> 
Maintainer: Julian Flesch <j.flesch@dkfz-heidelberg.de> 
Description: Wasserstein distance based functions and tests for detecting differential distributions in one-dimensional data. Includes Utilities for Wasserstein distance calculation, a statistical test, and a specialized test applicable to scRNA expression data.
